{"title":"Twisted nightmares from Anatoly Fomenko","date":"2019/01/24","author":"slw","body":[{"type":0,"content":"The artist"},{"type":2,"content":"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anatoly_Fomenko\">Anatoly Fomenko</a> is the live illustration of the following two facts: 1. mathematicians can do art and 2. renowned scientists can talk nonsense and put <i><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_Chronology_(Fomenko)\">substantial effort</a></i> into it. Fomenko's wicked mathematical landscapes are filled with ghastly wraiths, as emanations from an abyss that was stared at for too long. "},{"type":0,"content":"Seminal work"},{"type":4,"content":"assets/img/pieces/fomenko/bw/1.jpg"},{"type":4,"content":"assets/img/pieces/fomenko/bw/2.jpg"},{"type":5,"image1":"assets/img/pieces/fomenko/bw/3.jpg","image2":"assets/img/pieces/fomenko/bw/4.jpg"},{"type":5,"image1":"assets/img/pieces/fomenko/bw/5.jpg","image2":"assets/img/pieces/fomenko/bw/6.jpg"},{"type":0,"content":"Color works"},{"type":5,"image1":"assets/img/pieces/fomenko/color/1.jpg","image2":"assets/img/pieces/fomenko/color/2.jpg"},{"type":5,"image1":"assets/img/pieces/fomenko/color/5.jpg","image2":"assets/img/pieces/fomenko/color/4.jpg"},{"type":5,"image1":"assets/img/pieces/fomenko/color/3.jpg","image2":"assets/img/pieces/fomenko/color/7.jpg"},{"type":5,"image1":"assets/img/pieces/fomenko/color/6.jpg","image2":"assets/img/pieces/fomenko/color/8.jpg"},{"type":4,"content":"assets/img/pieces/fomenko/color/9.jpg"},{"type":4,"content":"assets/img/pieces/fomenko/color/10.jpg"},{"type":4,"content":"assets/img/pieces/fomenko/color/11.jpg"},{"type":4,"content":"assets/img/pieces/fomenko/color/12.jpg"}],"type":"pieces","id":4}